{"tid":1394824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷乜撚工，阻住哂香港發展！","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:33:57.000Z","uid":129988,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"485528f481868f80af40dbd447bca18b0565ca29","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母個閪就阻住地球轉！</span></span><br />\n叫你罷一日工要咗你全家條狗命呀？<br />\n成班細路命都唔要去檔子彈<br />\n你乜柒都唔做仲日日屌<br />\n就係差你班撚樣搞到我地罷工又唔夠人，唔夠影響力！<br />\n我話你聽<br />\n你係唔罷，咁撚鍾意返工嘛？<br />\n我之後就日9日塞你巴士塞你地鐵<br />\n我睇你點撚樣返工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班自私撚！我屌你老母！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef44e08fc565bf2596e88b11efca0acce6117391","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:18:12.000Z","msg":"係屌你呀仆街"},{"pid":"1e2d4eb211214fbd565b01767ca632e2316d644d","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"8月5見"},{"pid":"cfad3b6b5d1320ae993dc5c0365b66cead12c843","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"推到班仆街喺狗鐵走返出黎"},{"pid":"f6c6c2f4b80885d31e8de9fc29109e4d9abe36f1","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83964d0568e90e5e65ad1d2ae986e7ee22068f6b","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"星期一，齊罷工"},{"pid":"79cbbe317cc8a0570feaef3da23d95d2adeefabe","tid":1394824,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"屌死班自撚獅"},{"pid":"a56fba97ad0acf100203aef033b4cccbe71bf8e7","tid":1394824,"uid":258362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:27:21.000Z","ms